exthheader.author: David Gremillion
exthheader.description: “I’m not a typical Jedi,” Anakin said and ignited the lightsaber. The weapon felt natural in his hands, like he had been meant to have something like this his entire life. This wasn’t a simple stunsaber; this was a weapon of a Knight of the Jedi Order. “Then it begins,” Darth Maul sneered and the two charged each other.
exthheader.subject: prequel
